    "description": "<p>We are a local construction main contractor that is the market leader in PPVC technology &amp; methods. 5 out of our 6 projects are PPVC, and we are currently building the worlds tallest PPVC project - the Avenue South Residence. This project is 56 storeys tall and consists of 3,034 modules. All 3,034 modules were installed after the circuit breaker and completed in 20 months.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We are a design and build contractor and we are trusted by our clients to provide value engineering in all our projects. Our team is young and fresh graduates are encouraged to apply. One of our Project Managers is only 34 years old!</p>",
